title: Great experiences are found here at Signature Pointe Apartments!
posting_body: ['25102 62nd Avenue South, Kent, WA 98032', 'Signature Pointe Apartments lies alongside the Green River in Kent and is surrounded by tall evergreen trees.', 'The community offers many amenities for residents to enjoy year-round, from outdoor tennis courts, playgrounds, and fire pits, to indoor fitness centers and pools.', "You'll always find something to keep you busy here at Signature Pointe.", 'Apartment Features:', 'Over-sized Walk-In Closets', 'Built-In Bookshelves', 'Separate Dining Room', 'Top Floor Units Feature 19-ft Ceilings', 'Double Sinks', 'Microwave', 'Community Features:', 'Bordered by the Interurban Trail', 'Close to Schools, Restaurants, & Shops', 'Heated Indoor Pool, Sauna, & Spa', 'Flexible Monthly Payments with Flex Rent', 'Views of Mount Rainier', 'Quick Access to Major Freeways', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
